    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Advocates for or experts in architectural conservation, which is the practice of preserving the integrity of built objects, directed toward the long-term safekeeping of architectural heritage.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
